%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20attack%20on%20Ukraine%20market%20kills%20five%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775308416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa103%2Flive%2Fc0c0df90-3018-11f1-b297-95b0a0a8331e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp869m2gzr0o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Russian%20drone%20hit%20a%20busy%20spot%20in%20the%20southern%20Ukrainian%20town%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20injuring%20another%2021%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp869m2gzr0o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20I%20moved%20abroad%2C%20I%20left%20my%20parents%20behind%20in%20Mexico.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20our%20relationship%20to%20change%20so%20dramatically.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Santiago%20Barraza%20Lopez%20and%20his%20parents%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd8282e762ed6cfe449678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(middle)%20grew%20closer%20to%20his%20parents%20after%20moving%20abroad.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Santiago%20Barraza%20Lopez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20moved%20from%20Mexico%20to%20New%20York%20and%20then%20to%20London%2C%20leaving%20my%20parents%20behind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20abroad%2C%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20parents%20became%20more%20intentional.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20also%20now%20see%20my%20parents%20differently%20and%20celebrate%20all%20their%20sacrifices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Mexico%2C%20I%20never%20questioned%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20parents.%20In%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspanish-language-isnt-a-barrier-to-latinx-family-love-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELatino%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20closeness%20is%20the%20default%20setting.%20Parents%20are%20involved%20in%20everything%3A%20daily%20routines%2C%20big%20decisions%2C%20and%20emotional%20milestones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20at%20home%20well%20into%20adulthood%20wasn't%20unusual%2C%20and%20neither%20was%20the%20constant%20presence%20of%20family.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20assumed%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20parents%20was%20simply%20%26quot%3Bgood.%26quot%3B%20It%20wasn't%20something%20I%20analyzed.%20It%20just%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20Mexico%20to%20pursue%20my%20career%20abroad%2C%20first%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-deli-infested-viral-mac-patty-saved-business-datz-deli-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20later%20in%20London%2C%20distance%20quietly%20began%20to%20change%20the%20dynamic%20between%20us.%20Being%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%20forced%20me%20to%20examine%20a%20relationship%20I%20had%20previously%20taken%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a787db1-8cde-42d2-bab9-210fc9e250b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDistance%20turned%20routine%20into%20intention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-vietnam-escape-loneliness-longing-hard-to-go-home-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoving%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20lived%20with%20my%20parents.%20Our%20relationship%20was%20woven%20into%20daily%20life%3A%20quick%20conversations%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20passing%20comments%20about%20work%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20small%20interactions%20that%20fill%20a%20household.%20None%20of%20it%20felt%20particularly%20meaningful%20at%20the%20time%20because%20it%20was%20simply%20constant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDistance%20stripped%20that%20away.%20Once%20I%20moved%20abroad%2C%20our%20relationship%20became%20something%20that%20had%20to%20be%20scheduled.%20Calls%20were%20no%20longer%20casual%20interruptions%20in%20the%20day.%20They%20were%20deliberate%20moments.%20We%20chose%20to%20talk%2C%20and%20when%20we%20did%2C%20we%20actually%20paid%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisits%20changed%2C%20too.%20Seeing%20them%20once%20a%20year%2C%20sometimes%20twice%20if%20I%20was%20lucky%2C%20meant%20our%20time%20together%20carried%20weight.%20There%20was%20no%20room%20to%20waste%20a%20day%20arguing%20about%20something%20trivial.%20Those%20visits%20became%20about%20being%20present.%20And%20during%20the%20long%20months%20in%20between%2C%20the%20distance%20gave%20me%20space%20to%20reflect%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-relationship-with-parents-felt-like-adult-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparent-child%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ways%20I%20never%20had%20before%2C%20both%20the%20good%20parts%20and%20the%20complicated%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprised%20me%20most%20was%20how%20much%20I%20started%20to%20notice%20what%20I%20had%20never%20said.%20There%20were%20things%20I%20had%20always%20meant%20to%20tell%20them%2C%20gratitude%20I%20had%20assumed%20was%20obvious%2C%20pride%20I%20thought%20didn't%20need%20spelling%20out.%20Distance%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20the%20obvious%20things%20are%20often%20the%20ones%20that%20go%20unspoken%20the%20longest.%20I%20started%20saying%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ac72f50-7a62-48c3-b051-1cbce34127cc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20on%20my%20own%20helped%20me%20better%20understand%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20I%20left%20Mexico%20as%20an%20adult%20but%20didn't%20truly%20feel%20like%20one%20until%20I%20lived%20abroad.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20everything%3A%20rent%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvice-for-h1b-visa-holders-traveling-internationally-lawyer-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimmigration%20paperwork%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20building%20a%20life%20in%20a%20place%20where%20nothing%20was%20familiar.%20Independence%20stopped%20being%20an%20idea%20and%20became%20a%20daily%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20changed%20how%20I%20saw%20my%20parents.%20Many%20of%20the%20decisions%20I%20had%20once%20questioned%20began%20to%20make%20more%20sense.%20I%20started%20to%20see%20them%20not%20just%20as%20my%20parents%2C%20but%20as%20people%20navigating%20their%20own%20pressures%2C%20limitations%2C%20and%20fears%20while%20trying%20to%20raise%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20perspective%20came%20empathy.%20Some%20of%20the%20things%20I%20once%20held%20onto%20as%20frustrations%20started%20to%20feel%20smaller.%20Living%20far%20away%20didn't%20erase%20the%20past%2C%20but%20it%20made%20forgiveness%20easier%20and%20understanding%20more%20natural%20for%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20something%20humbling%20about%20realizing%20your%20parents%20sacrificed%20everything%20so%20you%20could%20one%20day%20have%20the%20audacity%20to%20leave.%20They%20built%20a%20life%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandparents-raising-grandchildren-retirement-social-security-financially-draining-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20a%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20poured%20everything%20into%20their%20kids%20so%20they%20could%20grow%20up%20and%20move%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I%20know%20what%20it%20actually%20takes%20to%20be%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20they%20did%20all%20of%20that%20while%20raising%20three%20kids%20who%20had%20no%20idea%20any%20of%20it%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a479c003-6e66-4ea6-a472-56dd45d78e04%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDistance%20didn't%20weaken%20our%20relationship%3B%20it%20clarified%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20expect%20was%20to%20notice%20how%20much%20they%20had%20changed%2C%20too.%20My%20parents%20are%20not%20the%20same%20people%20I%20left%20behind.%20They've%20gotten%20older%20in%20the%20small%2C%20slow%20ways%20you%20only%20notice%20when%20you%20haven't%20seen%20someone%20in%20months.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-lived-abroad-canada-europe-not-great-drawbacks-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiving%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20forced%20me%20to%20stop%20holding%20them%20in%20a%20fixed%20image%20and%20start%20seeing%20them%20as%20people%20still%20in%20motion%2C%20still%20figuring%20things%20out%2C%20just%20like%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20in%20that%20shift%2C%20something%20opened%20up.%20The%20conversations%20got%20warmer.%20The%20visits%20got%20fuller.%20We%20became%20more%20honest%20about%20how%20much%20we%20mean%20to%20each%20other%2C%20in%20ways%20that%20felt%20almost%20impossible%20when%20we%20were%20all%20just%20moving%20through%20the%20same%20house%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20abroad%20gave%20me%20something%20I%20never%20expected%3A%20the%20ability%20to%20see%20my%20parents%20more%20clearly.%20And%20what%20I%20found%2C%20when%20I%20finally%20looked%2C%20was%20that%20the%20love%20had%20always%20been%20there%2C%20deeper%20and%20more%20unconditional%20than%20I%20ever%20gave%20it%20credit%20for.%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20every%20mile%20between%20us%2C%20because%20it%20taught%20me%20to%20never%20take%20for%20granted%20the%20people%20who%20have%20loved%20me%20the%20longest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-abroad-relationship-with-parents-changed-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775308021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd82996a864f6fcd7bc835%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-abroad-relationship-with-parents-changed-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20left%20Mexico%20and%20