g%20window%2C%20lights%2C%20temperature%20controls%2C%20and%20a%20closet%20so%20small%20Amtrak%20barely%20managed%20to%20write%20%26quot%3BCloset%26quot%3B%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20closet%20we%20found%20two%20washcloths%20and%20enough%20space%20to%20squeeze%20in%20our%20jackets.%20There%20was%20a%20small%20area%20beneath%20it%20that%20fit%20our%20shoes%20and%20a%20small%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20able%20to%20fit%20all%20of%20our%20things%20inside%20the%20space.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bags%20on%20Amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9f05b58f1f0f9336c7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20we%20slid%20our%20backpacks%20and%20travel%20bags%20under%20the%20seats.%20At%20night%2C%20when%20those%20seats%20folded%20down%20into%20a%20bed%2C%20our%20bags%20ended%20up%20wedged%20between%20the%20bed%20and%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunset%20Limited%20left%20Los%20Angeles%20at%2010%20p.m.%2C%20so%20when%20we%20boarded%2C%20the%20roomette%20was%20already%20transformed%20into%20sleeping%20quarters.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20find%20a%20bathroom%20and%20get%20ready%20for%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20shared%20bathrooms%20were%20just%20fine%2C%20but%20not%20perfect.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20sink%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9f0e98a37a4841f3398%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20offers%20full%20bedroom%20upgrades%20which%20come%20with%20a%20private%20bathroom%20and%20shower%2C%20but%20we%20couldn't%20justify%20paying%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20more%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20roomette%20passengers%20share%20a%20shower%20room%20and%20public%20bathrooms%20%E2%80%94%20in%20our%20car%2C%20I%20counted%20one%20upstairs%20and%20three%20downstairs.%20At%20least%20one%20was%20always%20available%20when%20we%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bathrooms%20were%20just%20fine%2C%20though%20the%20toilet's%20loud%2C%20dramatic%20sucking%20sound%20during%20each%20flush%20was%20a%20bit%20jarring%2C%20and%20it%20was%20tricky%20to%20use%20the%20small%20sink%20basin%20without%20getting%20puddles%20on%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20also%20found%20out%20the%20hard%20way%20when%20somebody%20almost%20walked%20in%20on%20her%20that%20she%20had%20to%20pull%20the%20bathroom%20door%20shut%20and%20muscle%20the%20lock%20to%20the%20right%2C%20like%20she%20was%20sealing%20an%20airlock%2C%20or%20the%20%26quot%3Boccupied%26quot%3B%20light%20wouldn't%20turn%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20limited%20counter%20space%20in%20these%20bathrooms%2C%20so%20I%20suggest%20bringing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-toiletry-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20toiletry%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20loop%20that%20you%20can%20hang%20it%20on%20the%20door%20hook.%20You'll%20thank%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shower%20room%2C%20located%20next%20to%20the%20lower-level%20bathrooms%2C%20had%20a%20fold-down%20changing%20table%2C%20small%20seat%20area%2C%20counter%20space%2C%20and%20a%20handheld%20shower%20head%20that%20swayed%20with%20the%20train.%20I%20kept%20it%20aimed%20away%20from%20the%20shower%20door%20to%20avoid%20enacting%20Noah's%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWater%20pressure%3F%20Not%20great%2C%20but%20adequate.%20Water%20temperature%3F%20Surprisingly%20excellent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20provided%20us%20with%20towels%20and%20a%20wrapped%20bar%20of%20soap%2C%20but%20no%20shampoo%20or%20conditioner.%20You'll%20probably%20want%20to%20pack%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20meals%20were%20even%20better%20than%20I%20expected.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandwiches%20and%20chips%20on%20plates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9f0e98a37a4841f3399%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-roomettes-long-train-ride-expensive-not-worth-it-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eperks%20of%20a%20sleeper%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20all%20meals%20are%20included%3A%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20dinner%2C%20and%20dessert.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20brought%20a%20bag%20of%20snacks%20but%20hardly%20touched%20them%20because%20the%20meals%20were%20filling%20and%20quite%20tasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20the%20three-egg%20omelet%2C%20chicken%20sausage%2C%20and%20French%20toast%20for%20breakfast%2C%20Beyond%20Meat%20burger%20for%20lunch%2C%20and%20the%20chicken%20and%20salmon%20for%20dinner.%20They%20were%20all%20yummy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20enjoyed%20the%20steak%20and%20the%20burger%2C%20and%20we%20both%20loved%20the%20desserts%20%E2%80%A6%20maybe%20a%20little%20too%20much!%20The%20cheesecake%20and%20brownies%20served%20with%20each%20dinner%20were%20too%20delicious%20to%20pass%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ate%20breakfast%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-dining-car-surprising-things-from-frequent-traveler-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edining%20car%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20strangers%2C%20and%20had%20lunch%20and%20dinner%20delivered%20to%20our%20roomette%20at%20no%20extra%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20at%20our%20roomette's%20small%20fold-down%20table%20was%20convenient%2C%20though%20its%20cupholders%20could%20use%20some%20improvement.%20They're%20not%20very%20deep%2C%20so%20my%20drinks%20almost%20went%20flying%20whenever%20the%20train%20jerked.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20times%2C%20the%20ride%20felt%20almost%20unbearable%20and%20laughably%20wild.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20water%20and%20grass%20around%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9efe98a37a4841f3396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20prepared%20us%20for%20the%20true%20sounds%20and%20motions%20of%20the%20train.%20At%20slow%20speeds%2C%20the%20ride%20is%20relatively%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20I%20thought%20my%20butt%20might%20fall%20asleep%20after%20sitting%20for%20so%20long%2C%20but%20we%20brought%20a%20couple%20fleece%20blankets%20and%20sat%20on%20our%20pillows%20to%20cushion%20the%20ride.%20I%20wore%20sweats%20or%20pajamas%20and%20kicked%20off%20my%20shoes%20while%20in%20the%20roomette%2C%20because%20relaxation%20is%20key%20to%20a%20long%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20train%20is%20going%20fast%2C%20though%2C%20we%20felt%20some%20jostling.%20As%20it%20reached%20top%20speeds%2C%20being%20a%20passenger%20felt%20like%20a%20full-body%20contact%20sport.%20Think%3A%20roller%20coaster%20meets%20endless%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeware%20of%20sudden%20sways%20that%20might%20throw%20your%20head%20into%20the%20viewing%20window%2C%20tight%20hallways%20that%20require%20timing%20and%20balance%20to%20navigate%2C%20and%20the%20ever-present%20symphony%20of%20rattles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESleeping%20was%20quite%20challenging%20for%20us%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20of%20Amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9efe98a37a4841f3394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20top%20speed%2C%20the%20upper%20bunk%2C%20according%20to%20my%20girlfriend%2C%20felt%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20slightly%20padded%20board%20stuck%20inside%20a%20washing%20machine.%20The%20bottom%20bunk%20has%20the%20same%20thin%20mattress%20but%20it%20was%20cushioned%20by%20the%20folded%20down%20seats%20and%20best%20for%20taller%20passengers%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20left%20Los%20Angeles%20Union%20Station%2C%20the%20train%20transformed%20into%20a%20noise%20machine%3A%20Train%20horns%2C%20rattles%2C%20and%20sounds%20that%20might%20haunt%20my%20dreams%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELight%20sleepers%20may%20want%20to%20bring%20industrial-grade%20earplugs%2C%20sleep%20aids%2C%20or%20noise-canceling%20headphones.%20Seriously%2C%20the%20ride%20felt%20so%20extreme%20at%20times%20that%20I%20could%20only%20laugh%2C%20because%20what%20else%20can%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnytime%20the%20train%20stopped%2C%20I%20took%20advantage%20of%20that%20silence%20to%20sleep%20or%20get%20out%20and%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20can%20get%20a%20little%20stuffy%20and%20nothing%20beats%20the%20fresh%20air.%20During%20longer%20stops%2C%20we%20took%20short%20walks%20and%20gazed%20at%20cities%20we've%20never%20visited%2C%20like%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ride%20went%20by%20surprisingly%20quickly%2C%20though%2C%20and%20I%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20views.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rolled%20hay%20in%20field%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9ef5b58f1f0f9336c77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222382%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20trip%2C%20I%20wondered%20how%20we%20were%20going%20to%20pass%20the%20many%20hours%20aboard%20the%20train.%20We%20brought%20a%20tablet%20to%20watch%20videos%2C%20but%20I%20found%20myself%20drawn%20to%20the%20spectacular%20scenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20just%20stare%20and%20take%20pictures%20of%20the%20vast%20desert%2C%20the%20mountains%2C%20forests%2C%20and%20farms%20growing%20cotton%20or%20sugarcane.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20nice%20to%20take%20in%20America%20from%20a%20new%20perspective.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Horses%20behind%20fence%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9ef58b5806618e7dfc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-small-towns-to-visit-in-us-frequent-traveler-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall%20historic%20towns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20different%20from%20the%20huge%20city%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20which%20we%20call%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciated%20the%20winding%20rivers%2C%20bridges%2C%20lakes%2C%20and%20amazing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flouisiana-travel-guide-the-best-of-the-bayou-state-2011-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebayous%20of%20Louisiana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20endless%20sky%20with%20billowing%20clouds%20and%20breathtaking%20sunsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20cannot%20see%20America%20like%20this%20from%20a%20plane.%20Little%20kids%20wave%20at%20the%20train.%20You%20wave%20back.%20For%20a%20moment%2C%20everything%20feels%20simple%20and%20connected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20the%20journey%20was%20worth%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we'd%20do%20it%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sun%20behind%20clouds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f9ef58b5806618e7dfc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarrin%20Rosenthal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20trains%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20expect%20the%20unexpected.%20Our%20eastbound%20train%20arrived%2030%20minutes%20early%2C%20but%20our%20westbound%20train%20arrived%20two%20hours%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20traveling%20almost%204%2C000%20miles%20and%20over%2092%20hours%20on%20the%20train%2C%20we'd%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-cross-country-train-trip-review-new-york-chicago-seattle-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECross-country%20train%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20roomette%20was%20about%20twice%20the%20cost%20of%20flying%20but%20was%20more%20than%20worth%20it.%20You%20can't%20put%20a%20price%20on%20quality%20time%20spent%20with%20someone%20you%20love.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20my%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20some%20sleep%2C%20ate%20well%2C%20laughed%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20saw%20the%20country%20in%20a%20way%20few%20people%20ever%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica%20is%20beautiful%2C%20complicated%2C%20and%20enormous.%20Most%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20full%20of%20ordinary%2C%20good%20people%20waving%20from%20their%20yards%20as%20you%20pass%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-beautiful-amtrak-train-routes-from-frequent-passenger-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20Amtrak%20trains%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20old.%20Yes%2C%20the%20beds%20feel%20thin%20enough%20to%20qualify%20as%20yoga%20mats.%20Yes%2C%20the%20ride%20is%20loud.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20survived%2C%20and%20learned%20that%20if%20you%20prepare%20properly%2C%20bring%20a%20sense%20of%20humor%2C%20and%20remember%20it's%20about%20the%20journey%2C%20not%20the%20speed%2C%20you%20too%20will%20want%20to%20do%20it%20all%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-roomette-long-train-ride-sunset-limited-cons-2026-4%5C%2