orn%2C%20my%20focus%20shifted%20away%20from%20the%20hobbies%20that%20defined%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20postpartum%20depression%20treatment%20plan%20consisted%20of%20an%20SSRI%2C%20therapy%2C%20and%20sharing%20my%20feelings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20recovered%20from%20PPD%20and%20cherish%20the%20love%20and%20connection%20I%20share%20with%20my%20son.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20six%20glorious%20weeks%20before%20our%20son%20arrived%2C%20I%20relished%20the%20delicious%20pleasure%20of%20total%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20Liv's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mom-struggled-performance-review-returning-maternity-leave-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernity%20leave%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20begun.%20Our%20living%20room%20speakers%20pumped%20out%20the%20groovy%20soundtrack%20of%20her%20favorite%20deckbuilding%20video%20game%2C%20Balatro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20late-winter%20chill%20nipping%20at%20my%20cheeks%20as%20I%20biked%20home%20from%20a%20twilight%20music%20photography%20gig.%20I%20cherished%20falling%20asleep%20next%20to%20Liv%20at%202%20a.m.%20and%20waking%20up%20for%20lunchtime.%20I%20remember%20kissing%20her%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsucking-in-while-pregnant-tiktoker-goes-viral-for-controversial-video-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epregnant%20belly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20strong%20kicks%20tickling%20my%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20suddenly%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20slow%20down.%20Our%20son's%20due%20date%20sneaked%20up%20on%20us%3B%20labor%20could%20begin%20at%20any%20time.%20My%20mind%20was%20cloudy%20with%20vague%2C%20shapeless%20apprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf1bbeab-bacc-4a03-a8b2-23109693f37d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20world%20darkened%20in%20a%20hospital%20room%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20as%20prepared%20as%20we%20could%20have%20been.%20Liv%20and%20I%20read%20books%2C%20watched%20videos%2C%20and%20attended%20classes.%20Our%20tiny%20nursery%20corner%20was%20stocked%20and%20ready.%20We%20drove%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20our%20scheduled%20induction%2C%20Manhattan%20mostly%20asleep%20in%20the%20early%20dawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20a%20hospital%20room%20at%203%20am%2C%20our%20careful%20birthing%20plan%20seemed%20to%20shatter.%20Pitocin%2C%20the%20synthetic%20hormone%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Finduce-labor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einduce%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pumped%20through%20Liv's%20bloodstream%2C%20denying%20her%20the%20soothing%20effects%20of%20natural%20oxytocin.%20Her%20epidural%2C%20the%20anesthesia%20delivered%20inside%20her%20spinal%20canal%20through%20a%20plastic%20tube%2C%20partially%20failed.%20She%20could%20feel%20everything%2C%20and%20all%20I%20could%20do%20was%20squeeze%20her%20hand.%20My%20wife%2C%20the%20strongest%20human%20I%20know%2C%20screamed%20in%20pain%20I%20will%20never%20understand%20as%20our%20son%20entered%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20a%20hopeless%2C%20joyless%20shadow%20crawled%20through%20my%20soul.%20All%20of%20this%20effort%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20and%20pain%20was%20for%20a%20fleshy%20alien%20who%20barely%20looked%20like%20me%2C%20redirected%20every%20second%20of%20my%20free%20time%2C%20physically%20hurt%20my%20wife%2C%20stole%20her%20attention%20away%20from%20me%2C%20and%20kept%20me%20awake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quickly%20lost%20myself%20because%20I%20had%20no%20more%20time%20for%20the%20hobbies%20that%20make%20me%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20what%20reward%3F%20He%20couldn't%20love%20me.%20When%20he%20started%20to%20smile%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%20was%20anything%20more%20than%20involuntary%20muscle%20contractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22310dd98e-e459-450c-82d1-2500cb34ca9b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20power%20of%20empathy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20physician%20listened%20to%20my%20symptoms%20and%20named%20the%20disorder%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-long-does-postpartum-depression-last%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epostpartum%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20SSRI%20antidepressant%20had%20worked%20to%20pull%20me%20out%20of%20a%20previous%20pit%2C%20so%20my%20doctor%20prescribed%20me%20Lexapro.%20The%20second%20half%20of%20my%20treatment%20plan%20included%20a%20promise%20that%20I%20would%20share%20the%20true%20depth%20of%20my%20feelings%20with%20other%20people.%20Without%20my%20doctor%20validating%20my%20words%2C%20I%20may%20not%20have%20recovered%20from%20PPD%20as%20quickly%20as%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20a%20wonderful%2C%20compassionate%20partner%20and%20mother-in-law%20who%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20undergoing%20their%20own%20intense%20transformations%2C%20had%20an%20overflowing%20capacity%20to%20support%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20son%20was%20five%20weeks%20old%2C%20I%20spent%20five%20quiet%20days%20alone%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-new-york-city-different-than-visiting-lessons-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20visiting%20the%20movie%20theater%20and%20biking%20across%20the%20George%20Washington%20Bridge.%20This%20healing%20taste%20of%20my%20previous%20life%20gave%20me%20the%20momentum%20to%20be%20a%20better%20father%20and%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223dce5abd-2218-4730-933b-1ea7b3fbde1a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESharing%20my%20authentic%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20doctor%20encouraged%2C%20I%20shared%20my%20story%20with%20fathers-to-be%20at%20a%20weekly%20dad%20class.%20I%20spoke%20with%20vulnerability%20and%20honored%20my%20lived%20experiences.%20While%20every%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-told-something-about-parenting-that-has-stuck-with-me-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparenting%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20unique%2C%20we%20share%20a%20surprising%20number%20of%20common%20thoughts%2C%20feelings%2C%20and%20questions%20that%20deserve%20to%20be%20discussed%20but%20often%20aren't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndividual%20and%20couples%20therapy%20also%20yielded%20valuable%20coping%20tools%20for%20navigating%20the%20rough%2C%20novel%20transitions%20of%20parenthood.%20These%20were%20safe%20spaces%20to%20voice%20my%20deepest%2C%20scariest%20thoughts%20to%20a%20third%20party%20invested%20in%20our%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20son%20grew%2C%20milestone%20after%20incredible%20milestone%2C%20it%20became%20increasingly%20easier%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20others%20about%20my%20trials%20as%20a%20parent.%20I%20learned%20that%20almost%20everyone%20is%20willing%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20challenges%20related%20to%20sleep%2C%20coparenting%2C%20self-worth%2C%20burnout%2C%20or%20tantrums.%20These%20conversations%20comprise%20the%20crux%20of%20healing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bc678ac-ff95-44cb-a665-2fdfcb7a12cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrength%20for%20every%20season%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recently%20celebrated%20our%20son's%20second%20birthday.%20In%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20he's%20experienced%20yet%20another%20massive%20physical%20and%20mental%20growth%20spurt%2C%20accompanied%20by%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexercises-for-behavior-makeover-after-getting-job-promotion-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebehavioral%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20his%20afternoon%20nap%20is%20no%20longer%20guaranteed.%20As%20a%20stay-at-home%20dad%2C%20this%20extends%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20I%20work%20from%2010%20to%2012%2C%20including%20two%20extra%20hours%20spent%20with%20a%20tired%20toddler%20stumbling%20around%20the%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20what's%20next%2C%20but%20I%20know%20this%20exhausting%20season%20won't%20last.%20That's%20the%20difference%20between%20my%20mindset%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20today%3A%20This%20time%2C%20I%20have%20hope%20for%20the%20future.%20It's%20a%20future%20full%20of%20love%2C%20irreplaceable%20moments%2C%20and%20sudden%20shifts%20that%20change%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-experienced-postpartum-depression-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775305621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ce9ab2e762ed6cfe449aa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-experienced-postpartum-depression-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20thought%20I%20was%20prepared%20when%20my%20son%20was%20born%2C%20but%20I%20was%20suddenly%20hit%20with%20a%20dark%20cloud.%20This%20baby%20took%20away%20my%20identity%20and%20hurt%20my%20wife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Zachary%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-experienced-postpartum-depression-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Failed%20Attempt%20Last%20Year%2C%20Delhi%20Eyes%20Artificial%20Rain%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22IIT%20Kanpur%20has%20sought%20permission%20to%20conduct%20cloud%20seeding%20trials%20between%20April%20and%20June%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775305231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-10%2Fpo213qnc_cloud-seeding_625x300_28_October_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcloud-seeding-after-failed-attempt-last-year-delhi-eyes-artificial-rain-again-11310941%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IIT%20Kanpur%20has%20sought%20permission%20to%20conduct%20cloud%20seeding%20trials%20between%20April%20and%2