in%20Chicago%2C%20but%20I%20think%20Pontiac%2C%20Illinois%2C%20is%20the%20best%20place%20to%20officially%20get%20your%20bearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bob%20Waldmire%20Experience%2C%20located%20in%20the%20same%20complex%20as%20the%20Route%2066%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20%26amp%3B%20Museum%2C%20is%20the%20best%20place%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20road's%20most%20famous%20explorer.%20A%20nomadic%20artist%2C%20Waldmire%20used%20a%20VW%20bus%20and%20%26quot%3Broad%20yacht%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20converted%20double-decker%20school%20bus%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20studio%20on%20wheels%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20OG%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrew-up-as-van-lifer-hated-it-travel-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evan%20lifers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnap%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20iconic%20Route%2066%20Shield%20Mural%20before%20driving%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20south%20to%20Livingston%2C%20Illinois%2C%20home%20of%20the%20Pink%20Elephant%20Antique%20Mall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20historic%20building%2C%20once%20a%20high%20school%2C%20offers%20just%20about%20everything%20you%20could%20ask%20for%3A%20Alongside%20the%20massive%20maze%20of%20trinkets%20and%20goods%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20sweet%20treats%20at%20the%20Mother%20Road%20Fudge-n-Candy%20and%20eat%20a%20meal%20at%20the%20retro%20Twistee%20Treat%20Diner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20donned%20my%20best%20%26quot%3BGrease%26quot%3B%20getup%20and%20took%20advantage%20of%20all%20the%20photo%20ops%20there%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20including%20an%20oversize%20ice-cream%20cone%2C%20a%20giant%20UFO%2C%20and%20a%20bubblegum-pink%20elephant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20driving%20toward%20Missouri%2C%20and%20you'll%20approach%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECahokia%20Mounds%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funesco-world-heritage-sites-us-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20loved%20exploring%20the%20archaeological%20remains%20of%20the%20largest%20pre-Columbian%20city%20north%20of%20Mexico%20by%20walking%20the%20self-guided%20earth%20mound%20trails%2C%20then%20popping%20into%20the%20Interpretive%20Center%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aba00831-1bbe-4366-8b2f-8e47a918822c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHead%20to%20Amarillo%2C%20Texas%2C%20for%20steaks%20the%20size%20of%20your%20head%20and%20oversize%20art%20to%20match%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20Big%20Texan%20in%20Amarillo%2C%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cab2ea8373a547629c7b47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3ELauren%20Durie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Texas-sized%20Route%2066%20fun%2C%20the%20Big%20Texan%20Steak%20Ranch%20%26amp%3B%20Brewery%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20small%20town%20than%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20best%20known%20for%20the%2072-ounce%20steak%20challenge%2C%20which%20began%20in%20the%201960s%20as%20a%20competition%20between%20cowboys%20to%20see%20who%20could%20out-carb%20each%20other.%20Now%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20open%20to%20anyone%20willing%20to%20attempt%20the%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinish%20the%20spread%20in%20under%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20it's%20free%3B%20fail%2C%20and%20it's%20%2472.%20Nearly%20100%2C000%20people%20have%20tried%2C%20with%20roughly%2010%2C000%20succeeding.%20Oh%2C%20and%20anyone%20attempting%20the%20challenge%20is%20live%20streamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kindly%20passed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurant%20serves%20regular%20meals%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20commend%20anyone%20who%20gives%20it%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20more%20to%20explore%20at%20Big%20Texan%2C%20too%2C%20including%20live%20music%2C%20a%20shooting%20gallery%2C%20and%20covered%20wagons%20and%20cabins%20for%20overnight%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D