-cars-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney's%20%26quot%3BCars%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wild%20burros%20descend%20from%20pack%20animals%20used%20by%20miners%20during%20the%20Gold%20Rush%20years.%20Local%20shops%20sell%20bags%20of%20food%2C%20and%20if%20you%20feed%20them%2C%20they'll%20quickly%20try%20to%20become%20your%20best%20friends.%20(Fair%20warning%3A%20They%20%3Cem%3Edo%3C%2Fem%3E%20nip%2C%20and%20one%20almost%20ripped%20my%20dress.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETourists%20are%20encouraged%20to%20feed%20and%20photograph%20the%20burros%20as%20long%20as%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20sticker%20on%20their%20head%2C%20which%20means%20they've%20been%20tagged%20as%20a%20baby%20or%20as%20needing%20a%20special%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20your%20visit%20right%2C%20and%20you%20could%20also%20end%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20reenacted%20shootout%20on%20Main%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20found%20equally%20thrilling%20and%20unhinged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20another%20outlaw%20experience%20along%20Route%2066%2C%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%20Railway%20in%20nearby%20Williams%2C%20Arizona%2C%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvintage-retro-train-travel-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evintage%20train%20ride%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20national%20park%20with%20%26quot%3Bbandits%26quot%3B%20as%20carmates.%20A%20road%20trip%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20characters%20you%20meet%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-cities-to-stop-route-66-texas-illinois-arizona-towns-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775304541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cab4ba8373a547629c7b58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-cities-to-stop-route-66-texas-illinois-arizona-towns-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%2