Tulsi%20Gabbard%20and%20commerce%20secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick.%20The%20administration%20faces%20pressure%20to%20project%20strength%20and%20address%20economic%20worries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-mulls-big-cabinet-shake-up-as-iran-war-backlash-deepens-report%2Farticleshow%2F130017506.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-mulls-big-cabinet-shake-up-as-iran-war-backlash-deepens-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F130017506.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-mulls-big-cabinet-shake-up-as-iran-war-backlash-deepens-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F130017506.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20mediocre%20worker%20is%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bar%20for%20keeping%20your%20job%20just%20went%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20illustration%20of%20an%20oversized%20handing%20reaching%20through%20the%20frame%20and%20squeezing%20an%20office%20worker%20at%20his%20desk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d025abc02a678bd7e47f07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20are%20replacing%20lower-performing%20workers%20with%20stronger%20talent%20to%20boost%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20one%20way%20businesses%20are%20optimizing%20their%20workforces%20as%20hiring%20budgets%20tighten.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trend%20is%20playing%20out%20from%20early-career%20roles%20to%20the%20C-suite.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20hiring%20budgets%20constrained%2C%20some%20companies%20are%20finding%20a%20different%20way%20to%20bring%20in%20talent%3A%20replacing%20workers%20with%20better%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20just%20no%20appetite%20for%20mediocrity%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brent%20Orsuga%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20and%20logistics%20recruiting%20firm%20Pinnacle%20Growth%20Advisors.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20he's%20seen%20many%20of%20his%20clients%20quietly%20replace%20employees%20rather%20than%20grow%20headcount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20looking%20at%20what%20they%20have%20and%20being%20like%2C%20'I%20want%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%2C'%26quot%3B%20Orsuga%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20example%20of%20a%20company%20with%2010%20sales%20reps%20that%20is%20looking%20to%20boost%20performance%2C%20he%20said.%20They%20could%20expand%20the%20team.%20But%20it's%20often%20more%20affordable%20to%20identify%20the%20lowest-performing%20reps%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20better%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20new%20employees%20cost%20a%20bit%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20upgrading%20isn't%20new%2C%20Orsuga%20said%20that%202025%20was%20the%20biggest%20year%20he's%20seen%20for%20the%20trend%20in%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20recruiting%20world.%20He%20calls%20it%20%26quot%3Bbullseye%20hiring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20every%20seat%20matters%2C%20so%20I've%20got%20to%20hit%20a%20bullseye%20and%20get%20the%20right%20person%20in%20the%20right%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fwhat-the-job-market-freeze-means-for-workforce-in-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHiring%20has%20slowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20recently%2C%20due%20to%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20cost-cutting%2C%20and%20AI%20adoption.%20In%20February%2C%20the%20hiring%20rate%20fell%20to%203.1%25%20%E2%80%94%20a%20modern%20low%20matched%20only%20by%20the%20pandemic%20and%20early%20recovery%20from%20the%20Great%20Recession.%20Three%20recruiters%20across%20tech%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20logistics%20said%20that%20when%20companies%20do%20hire%2C%20it%20can%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20an%20existing%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20driving%20forces%20behind%20the%20shift%2C%20which%20they%20said%20is%20playing%20out%20from%20early-career%20roles%20to%20the%20C-suite%2C%20is%20a%20push%20to%20maximize%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-investor-day-resist-hiring-headcount-ai-efficiencies-jamie-dimon-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20dollar%20spent%20on%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20hiring%20budgets%20tighten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5a1d8b0-049b-4f24-b689-84a9d72e57da%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20need%20to%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20job%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20job%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20clients%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20existing%20employees%20turn%20to%20confidential%20searches%2C%20said%20Lindsay%20Myketey%2C%20a%20recruiter%20at%20Cella%20by%20Randstad%20Digital%20who%20focuses%20on%20mid-%20to%20senior-level%20marketing%20and%20technology%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20as%20roles%20evolve%2C%20companies%20may%20replace%20workers%20for%20several%20reasons%2C%20from%20underperformance%20to%20gaps%20in%20skills%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-google-jpmorgan-make-ai-performance-reviews-goals-raises-promotions-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethose%20related%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20added%20that%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-career-squeeze-slow-hiring-no-time-for-training-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanagers%20are%20taking%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20that%20companies%20might%20replace%20those%20who%20can't%20keep%20up.%20Sometimes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20employees%20are%20moved%20into%20different%20roles%20rather%20than%20let%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20replacement%20searches%20happen%20can%20vary%20by%20role%20and%20level.%20For%20senior%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20those%20paying%20at%20least%20%24100%2C000%20annually%20%E2%80%94%20Orsuga%20said%20companies%20might%20use%20headhunters%20to%20conduct%20confidential%20searches%20instead%20of%20publicly%20posting%20the%20role%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20helps%20avoid%20%26quot%3Bspooking%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20they're%20looking%20to%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20mid-level%20roles%2C%20he%20said%20companies%20use%20a%20mix%20of%20headhunters%20and%20job%20postings.%20Some%20are%20required%20to%20post%20roles%20externally%20for%20compliance%20reasons%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20because%20many%20employees%20share%20similar%20titles%2C%20a%20new%20posting%20can%20signal%20growth%20rather%20than%20a%20looming%20replacement.%20Orsuga%20added%20that%20some%20companies%20are%20%26quot%3Balways%20hiring%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20on%20new%20talent%20not%20necessarily%20to%20grow%20headcount%2C%20but%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-layoffs-cuts-underperformers-sra-spring-summer-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplace%20lower-performing%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20time.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20dynamic%20can%20disproportionately%20affect%20early-career%20workers%2C%20who%20may%20find%20themselves%20competing%20with%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-boosting-hiring-entry-level-engineers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecohorts%20of%20new%20graduates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20Orsuga%20said%2C%20high-performing%20employees%20are%20cut%20because%20they're%20too%20expensive.%20He%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20sports%20world%2C%20where%20many%20teams%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-professional-athletes-make-from-endorsement-deals-sponsorship-basketball-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoperate%20under%20a%20salary%20cap%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20only%20so%20much%20money%20to%20spend%2C%20and%20sometimes%20that%20means%20moving%20on%20from%20a%20talented%2C%20highly-paid%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acc51440-0a9f-452a-97b9-9093fe6abce6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExecutives%20aren't%20immune%20to%20replacement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20regular%20workers%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20clear%20whether%20they%20were%20replaced%20or%20simply%20caught%20up%20in%20cost-cutting.%20But%20at%20the%20top%20of%20organizations%2C%20the%20distinction%20is%20often%20clearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20roughly%2011%25%20of%20CEOs%20were%20replaced%20across%201%2C500%20of%20the%20largest%20public%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20executive-recruiting%20firm%20Spencer%20Stuart.%20That's%20the%20highest%20turnover%20rate%20since%202010%2C%20when%20the%20US%20was%20emerging%20from%20the%20Great%20Recession.%20The%20report%20pointed%20to%20greater%20market%20volatility%2C%20complex%20trade%20dynamics%2C%20and%20economic%20uncertainty%20as%20factors%20driving%20the%20increase%2C%20adding%20that%20investors%20and%20boards%20had%20%26quot%3Bless%20patience%20for%20CEOs%20overseeing%20weak%20growth%20and%20for%20those%20slow%20to%20transform%20their%20organizations%20for%20an%20AI-centric%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarun%20Inuganti%2C%20a%20recruiter%20focused%20on%20tech%20executive%20search%2C%20said%20that%20when%20his%20firm%2C%20Korn%20Ferry%2C%20is%20brought%20in%2C%20it's%20typically%20instructed%20to%20consider%20both%20internal%20and%20external%20candidates%2C%20with%20searches%20often%20taking%20about%2090%20days%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20talked%20to%20many%20clients%20of%20mine%20who've%20said%2C%20'We're%20just%20trying%20to%20have%20the%20best%20person%20in%20the%20role.%20We're%20just%20not%20adding%20headcount%20because%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20market.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20workers%20across%20the%20economy%2C%20layoffs%20remain%20low%20relative%20to%20historical%20levels.%20But%20Myketey%20said%20people%20shouldn't%20overlook%20the%20risk%20of%20replacement%20%E2%80%94%20and%20being%20pushed%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-find-work-employment-hiring-slowdown-careers-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenging%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20you%20have%20the%20job%2C%20you%20really%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20operating%20at%20a%20high%20level%2C%20like%20on%20the%20'good%20list%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-replacing-workers-executives-recruiters-hiring-slowdown-job-market-economy-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775299501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d025abc02a678bd7e47f07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-replacing-workers-executives-recruiters-hiring-slowdown-job-market-economy-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recruiters%20say%20companies%20are%20swapping%20out%20employees%20for%20more%20skilled%20or%20lower-cost%20talent%20as%20hiring%20slows%20and%20budgets%20tighten.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-replacing-workers-executives-recruiters-hiring-slowdown-job-market-economy-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20persevered%20through%20America's%20annoyance%20economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22customer%20ervice%20phone%20call%20annoyance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2c9c65b58f1f0f9336ad4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20won%20her%20tiff%20with%20the%20annoyance%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20without%20some%20sweat.%3Cp%3EXavier%20Lorenzo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20BI%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef84679e-5101-4303-beb5-fc75bc92b8c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutlasting%20the%20annoyance%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20popped%20off.%20As%20my%20husband%20picked%20it%20up%2C%20the%20handle%20on%20my%20beloved%2C%20buy-it-for-life%20carry-on%20suitcase%20flew%20right%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20(my%20bag)%20was%20only%20three%20years%20old%2C%20in%20great%20condition%20(or%20so%20I'd%20thought)%2C%20from%20a%20reputable%20brand%2C%20and%20had%20never%20even%20been%20checked%20at%20an%20airport.%20Yet%20my%20plans%20to%20travel%20with%20this%20%24300%20bag%20for%20decades%20had%20disappeared%20as%20quickly%20as%20the%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20all%20hope%20was%20lost%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20product%20warranty%20I'd%20registered%20for.%20Armed%20with%20photos%20of%20the%20damage%20and%20my%20receipt%2C%20I%20eventually%20tracked%20down%20and%20filled%20out%20the%20(very%20thorough)%20customer-support%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20days%2C%20and%20some%20back-and-forth%2C%20a%20nameless%20customer-support%20entity%20declared%20that%20my%20bag%20wasn't%20covered%20by%20a%20special%20plan%20that%20had%20expired%2C%20sent%20me%20a%20long%20list%20of%20reasons%20as%20to%20why%20they%20wouldn't%20help%20me%20even%20if%20it%20was%2C%20and%20offered%20me%20a%2015%25%20off%20coupon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20letting%20this%20company%20off%20the%20hook%20so%20easily.%20After%20several%20minutes%20of%20deep-diving%20on%20the%20company%20website%2C%20I%20was%20confident%20that%20my%20suitcase%20%3Cem%3Eshould%20be%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecovered%20by%20its%20lifetime%20warranty.%20I%20sent%20a%20detailed%20email%20in%20response%2C%20complete%20with%20screenshots%20from%20the%20company's%20own%20website%20as%20proof%20that%20my%20bag%20should%20be%20repaired%20or%20replaced%20on%20their%20dime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20I%20had%20received%20an%20email%20from%20a%20manager%20(with%20a%20name)%20and%20the%20shipping%20details%20for%20my%20brand-new%20replacement%20suitcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20won%2C%20but%20I'd%20suffered%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-customer-service-profit-annoyance-economy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerica's%20annoyance%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20it%2C%20spending%20my%20lunch%20break%20playing%20lawyer%20and%20collecting%20evidence%2C%20hoping%20a%20real%20person%20would%20answer%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20BI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjuliana-kaplan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuliana%20Kaplan%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20wrote%2C%20there's%20big%20money%20in%20companies%20exhausting%20and%20frustrating%20their%20consumers.%20If%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20mental%20energy%2C%20and%20verbal%20fights%20with%20unhelpful%20customer-service%20bots%20to%20cancel%20a%20subscription%2C%20make%20a%20return%2C%20or%2C%20in%20my%20case%2C%20have%20a%20warranty%20honored%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20companies%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20imagine%20how%20many%20others%20in%20my%20position%20just%20believed%20they%20had%20no%20path%20forward%20and%20accepted%20the%20measly%20coupon%20as%20a%20consolation%20prize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20old%20suitcase%3F%20I'm%20looking%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-tariffs-americans-learn-to-fix-things-repair-prices-savings-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20it%20repaired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20economy%2C%20I'm%20not%20letting%20a%20%24300%20bag%20go%20to%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-i-perservered-through-annoyance-economy-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775299081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cff1ff6a864f6fcd7bd348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-i-perservered-through-annoyance-economy-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20Saturday%20edition%20of%20Busi