s%20given%20Turnbull%20more%20flexibility%20to%20live%20the%20life%20she%20wants%2C%20which%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-new-country-after-living-on-sailboat-biggest-adjustments-challenges-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplenty%20of%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20managed%20to%20save%20loads%20of%20money%20and%20actually%20go%20traveling%2C%20which%20is%20something%20I%20definitely%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%20if%20I%20had%20a%20house%20and%20not%20a%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20notably%2C%20Turnbull%20spent%20a%20year%20traveling%20in%20Australia.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20her%20boat%20moored%20while%20she%20was%20away%2C%20and%20she%20used%20the%20skills%20she%20learned%20renovating%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F24-year-old-converted-mercedes-campervan-luxury-tiny-house-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturn%20a%20van%20into%20her%20temporary%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20year%20she%20spent%20traveling%20around%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ended%20up%20selling%20the%20van%20for%20more%20than%20I%20bought%20it%20for%20because%20I'd%20done%20all%20the%20renovations%2C%20so%20I%20think%20having%20done%20that%20on%20the%20boat%20really%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20do%20that%20in%20a%20van%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20became%20a%20full-time%20content%20creator%20with%20videos%20about%20her%20narrowboat%2C%20so%20it%20transformed%20her%20career%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20Turnbull%20loves%20the%20way%20her%20narrowboat%20has%20simplified%20her%20life.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20kitchen%20of%20a%20narrowboat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ce709dc02a678bd7e474c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETanglewood%20%26amp%3B%20Two%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETurnbull%20said%20the%20narrowboat%20lifestyle%20has%20helped%20her%20slow%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20really%2C%20really%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20appreciate%20the%20little%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20every%20day%20outside%2C%20and%20I%20make%20a%20point%20of%20doing%20it%20outside%20unless%20it's%20pouring%20down%20rain.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20you%20sit%20on%20the%20top%2C%20and%20you'll%20watch%20the%20sunset%20and%20appreciate%20those%20little%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20of%20a%20manual%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Turnbull%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20fill%20my%20water%20up%2C%20I%20have%20to%20fill%20my%20diesel%20up%20for%20my%20heating%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20empty%20my%20toilet.%20It%20makes%20you%20appreciate%20everything%20else%20a%20little%20bit%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20aren't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-quit-living-on-sailboat-full-time-moved-back-land-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echallenges%20of%20boat%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Turnbull%2C%20like%20keeping%20track%20of%20how%20the%20weather%20might%20impact%20the%20boat%2C%20walking%20her%20dog%20near%20the%20water%20in%20the%20bitter%20cold%20of%20winter%2C%20or%20making%20sure%20she%20plans%20far%20enough%20in%20advance%20to%20get%20gas%20for%20the%20boat.%20Still%2C%20Turnbull%20thinks%20the%20boat%20only%20adds%20to%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20biggest%20advocate%20for%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20because%20of%20the%20opportunities%20it's%20now%20given%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20completely%20changed%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A