stretched%20finances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp84z5r4d32o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2059-year-old%20man%20lost%2025%20pounds%20on%20Foundayo%2C%20the%20new%20GLP-1%20weight-loss%20pill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223061%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22foundayo%20pill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d00f38c02a678bd7e47e1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFoundayo%2C%20the%20new%20GLP-1%20weight%20loss%20pill%20from%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20on%20April%201.%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFoundayo%2C%20a%20new%20weight%20loss%20pill%20from%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20is%20the%20first%20oral%20GLP-1%20that%20doesn't%20require%20fasting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20clinical%20trials%2C%20people%20lost%20an%20average%20of%208-25%20pounds%20on%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20man%20who%20took%20the%20pill%20for%2018%20months%20said%20it%20helped%20reduce%20his%20appetite%2C%20and%20he%20lost%2025%20pounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20here.%20The%20first%20no-fuss%20once-daily%20GLP-1%20pill%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffoundayo-vs-zepbound-wegovy-rybelsus-cost-insurance-side-effects-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEli%20Lilly's%20Foundayo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20the%20type%202%20diabetes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsedentary-man-weight-loss-success-simple-strategies-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweight%20loss%20%3C%2Fa%3Eindustry.%20Until%20now%2C%20patients%20taking%20the%20new%20class%20of%20GLP-1%20drugs%20have%20had%20to%20choose%20from%20either%20a%20weekly%20injection%20that's%20stored%20in%20the%20refrigerator%2C%20like%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20or%20Zepbound%2C%20or%20swallow%20a%20once-daily%20pill%20that%20requires%20patients%20to%20take%20it%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-pills-coming-but-may-not-be-convenient-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eempty%20stomach%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20small%20glass%20of%20water%20(Rybelsus%20or%20Wegovy%20pill%2C%20from%20Novo%20Nordisk).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20medicine%2C%20generically%20called%20orforgipron%2C%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20potentially%20unlocking%20a%20worldwide%20market%20of%20millions%20more%20patients%20who%20want%20the%20convenience%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lillys-orforglipron-beats-novo-nordisk-glp1-pill-in-tests-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edaily%20pill%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethey%20can%20slot%20into%20their%20existing%20medicine%20regimen%2C%20at%20any%20hour%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2b164f5-6576-4741-a7bf-b7fa02ca7b96%5C%22%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20take%20Foundayo%3A%20less%20hunger%2C%20slower%20digestion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Salberg%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20patients%20to%20try%20the%20pill%20out%20in%20real%20life.%20The%2059-year-old%20from%20New%20Jersey%20got%20a%20sneak%20peek%20at%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20on%20this%20new%20medication%20when%20he%20participated%20in%20an%2018-month%20clinical%20trial%20Eli%20Lilly%20conducted%20in%202024%20and%202025%20to%20gauge%20safety%20and%20efficacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalberg%20heard%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclinical-trial-participant-pay-erase-credit-card-debt-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclinical%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20email.%20He%20had%20tried%20losing%20weight%20many%20times%20before%2C%20but%20nothing%20seemed%20to%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20doing%20things%20right%20with%20exercise%20and%20a%20balanced%20diet%2C%20but%20I%20was%20never%2C%20ever%20really%20satisfied%20with%20the%20weight%20management%20I%20was%20able%20to%20maintain%20on%20my%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Salberg%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20enrolled%20in%20the%20trial%2C%20hoping%20for%20something%20different.%20He%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20daily%20pill%20that%20he%20could%20take%20alongside%20his%20other%20prescription%20medications.%20It%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20slot%20this%20new%20routine%20into%20his%20existing%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20travel%20a%20lot%20for%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20already%20had%20oral%20medication%20I%20was%20taking%2C%20so%20it%20was%20just%20very%20simple%20to%20add%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22foundayo%20glp1%20bottle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cfe0896a864f6fcd7bd28d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFoundayo%20is%20the%20first%20GLP-1%20pill%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20at%20any%20time%20of%20day%2C%20regardless%20of%20when%20a%20patient%20had%20their%20last%20meal.%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20five%20days%20he%20was%20on%20the%20medication%2C%20Salberg%20didn't%20notice%20anything%20remarkable%20happening.%20The%20first%20time%20he%20noticed%20something%20different%20was%20at%20dinner%2C%20on%20that%20fifth%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20just%20having%20a%20good%20meal%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20roast%20chicken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20about%20a%20portion%2C%20and%20then%20realized%20I%20was%20perfectly%20satisfied.%20I%20didn't%20need%20any%20more%20food%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20just%20comfortably%20set%20it%20aside.%20Then%20I%20realized%3A%20wait%20a%20minute%2C%20I've%20never%20done%20that%20before!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22857986b7-0f17-4de5-a156-80eddda02e05%5C%22%3EHis%20biggest%20side%20effect%3A%20slow%20digestion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tiny%20salad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d004b26a864f6fcd7bd3da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeing%20full%20with%20less%20food%20was%20a%20surprise.%3Cp%3Egerenme%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESalberg%20said%20he%20could%20feel%20his%20digestive%20system%20slowing%20down%2C%20making%20him%20feel%20fuller%20faster%20than%20before.%20What%20used%20to%20be%20a%20normal%20portion%20was%20simply%20too%20much%20food%20now.%20It%20was%20surprising%2C%20he%20said%2C%20having%2050-plus%20years%20of%20eating%20habits%20shift%20like%20that%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1%20drugs%20work%20by%20mimicking%20a%20hunger-regulating%20hormone%20we%20produce%20naturally%20(called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ozempic-wegovy-actually-work-telling-brain-to-feel-full-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eglucagon-like%20peptide%201%3C%2Fa%3E)%20that%20makes%20us%20feel%20full.%20The%20drugs%20are%20more%20powerful%20than%20our%20own%20hunger%20hormone%2C%20though%2C%20lasting%20longer%2C%20slowing%20down%20our%20digestion%2C%20and%20improving%20blood%20sugar%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20common%20side%20effects%20of%20the%20drug%20patients%20experience%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENausea%20(in%2029-34%25%20of%20patients%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20dosage)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConstipation%20(22-25%25)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDiarrhea%20(21-23%25)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3Eand%20vomiting%20(13-24%25)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20Salberg%20committed%20to%20other%20healthy%20lifestyle%20changes.%20He%20made%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20roughly%20three%20days%20a%20week%20for%20a%20mix%20of%20cardio%20and%20strength%20training%2C%20which%20doctors%20generally%20recommend%20to%20patients%20on%20GLP-1%20drugs%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-drug-mimics-exercise-with-a-shot-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20prevent%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-drug-mimics-exercise-with-a-shot-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20muscle%20wasting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20he%20improved%20his%20diet%2C%20swapping%20out%20more%20red%20meat%20and%20saturated%20fats%20for%20lean%20proteins%20like%20roasted%20chicken%20or%20grilled%20fish%2C%20plus%20lots%20of%20vegetables%20on%20the%20side%2C%20a%20healthy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhelpful-advice-for-following-a-mediterranean-diet-from-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMediterranean-style%20diet%20%3C%2Fa%3Eplan%20many%20dietitians%20recommend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de7c5ba1-a5a6-49d7-bd1f-e6412bf601dc%5C%22%3EHe%20lost%2025%20pounds%20and%20has%20kept%20most%20of%20it%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20months%2C%20Salberg%20had%20lost%20seven%20pounds.%20The%20next%20month%2C%20he%20shed%20five%20more.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20he'd%20stabilized%20at%20a%20new%20weight%2C%2025%20pounds%20lighter%20than%20he'd%20been%20before.%20He%20tightened%20his%20belt%20loop%20up%20by%20two%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20absolutely%20helped%20with%20losing%20weight%2C%20there's%20no%20doubt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20trial%20was%20over%2C%20Salberg%20did%20notice%20his%20old%20appetite%20kick%20back%20in%2C%20after%20about%20six%20weeks%20without%20any%20medication%20in%20his%20system.%20But%20he%20said%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20most%20of%20the%20weight%20loss%20he%20accomplished%20on%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20little%20bit%20did%20come%20back%2C%20but%20nowhere%20close%20to%20where%20I%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20credits%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-maintenance-lessons-learned-4-years-after-fat-muscle-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweight%20maintenance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20continued%20portion%20control%20and%20healthy%20movement.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Foundayo%20is%20on%20the%20market%2C%20he's%20planning%20to%20chat%20to%20his%20doctor%20about%20possibly%20getting%20back%20on%20the%20medication.%20If%20it's%20covered%20by%20insurance%2C%20the%20pill%20could%20cost%20him%20as%20little%20as%20%2425%20a%20month.%20Eli%20Lilly%20is%20also%20selling%20the%20pill%20directly%20on%20its%20website%2C%20with%20cash%20pay%20prices%20of%20%24149%20to%20%24349%20a%20month%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20dose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-take-foundayo-new-weight-loss-pill-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775297341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cfe895c02a678bd7e47cbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-take-foundayo-new-weight-loss-pill-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20on%20Foundayo%2C%20the%20new%20GLP-1%20weight%20loss%20pill%20from%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20tend%20to%20feel%20full%20faster%2C%20and%20may%20experience%20nausea%2C%20constipation%2C%20or%20diarrhea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-take-foundayo-new-weight-loss-pill-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Pat%20Cummins%20left%20SR