%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-billionaire-alex-karp-ties-miami-mansion-purchase-hq-move-2026-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlex%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20people%20are%20spending%20big%20on%20waterfront%20properties%20in%20Miami.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20status%20symbol%20is%20helping%20them%20beat%20traffic%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EILandMiami%20offers%20mobile%20helipads%20that%20travel%20the%20waterways%20so%20billionaires%20can%20land%20near%20their%20own%20backyards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20is%20money%2C%20as%20the%20saying%20goes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20real%20estate%20agent%20Angel%20Nicolas'%20clientele%2C%20who%20are%20spending%20eight%20figures%20on%20homes%20in%20South%20Florida%2C%20time%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20a%20recent%20buyer%20wanted%20to%20tour%20homes%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Miami%2C%20and%20the%20Florida%20Keys%2C%20he%20knew%20a%20car%20or%20the%20Brightline%20wouldn't%20do.%20Instead%2C%20they%20traveled%20by%20helicopter%2C%20landing%20on%20a%20floating%20helipad%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20expensive%20thing%2C%20but%20time%20is%20the%20most%20valuable%20thing%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicolas%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20his%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-new-york-from-florida-things-that-surprised-me%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiami%20traffic%3C%2Fa%3E%20worse%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20in%202024%2C%20the%20average%20commuter%20in%20the%20city%20spent%2093%20hours%20in%20traffic%2C%20according%20to%20a%202025%20report%20from%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM's%20Transportation%20Institute%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20ultrawealthy%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20save%20their%20precious%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EILandMiami%20is%20offering%20a%20new%20solution%20that's%20becoming%20a%20hot%20commodity%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-billionaires-larry-page-spending-miami-homes-luxury-real-estate-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiami's%20new%20billionaire%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20longer%20do%20they%20have%20to%20spend%20an%20hour%20traveling%20to%20or%20from%20Miami's%20private%20airports%20to%20their%20homes%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-billionaires-moving-miami-indian-creek-coconut-grove-coral-gables-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIndian%20Creek%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Fisher%20Island.%20Instead%2C%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20it%20can%20take%20a%20five%20or%20six-minute%20helicopter%20ride%20to%20the%20water%20off%20their%20own%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20a%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20Miami%2C%20provides%20aquatic%2C%20mobile%20helipads%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20cost%3F%20About%20%241%2C000%20per%20minute%20%E2%80%94%20helicopter%20not%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20how%20much%20money%20is%20here%20and%20how%20many%20properties%20are%20on%20the%20water%20and%20how%20many%20people%20could%20potentially%20use%20the%20service%20due%20to%20the%20traffic%20and%20the%20way%20Miami%20was%20growing%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20Terris%2C%20ILandMiami's%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20some%20billionaires%20calling%20us%2C%20and%20then%20the%20wheel%20started%20to%20turn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20years%20for%20ILandMiami%2C%20founded%20in%202016%2C%20to%20launch%20its%20marine%20utility%20vehicles%2C%20MUVs%20for%20short%2C%20due%20to%20the%20complexities%20of%20building%20something%20that%20could%20handle%20large%20commercial%20helicopters%20and%20obtain%20Coast%20Guard%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20launched%20in%20January%20of%20last%20year%2C%20in%20time%20for%20the%20new%20influx%20of%20billionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20several%20of%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20people%2C%20including%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Larry%20Page%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsergey-brin-miami-purchase-allison-island-51-million-waterfront-property-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20spent%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20waterfront%20properties%20in%20Miami.%20The%20helipads%20have%20been%20spotted%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20where%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Jeff%20Bezos%20own%20homes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20expensive%20hotels%20like%20the%20Fontainebleau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Terris%20declined%20to%20mention%20specific%20customers%2C%20citing%20NDAs%2C%20he%20said%20that%20several%20have%20name%20recognition.%20They%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20people%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20would%20typically%20land%20their%20helicopters%20directly%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-billionaires-buying-superyachts-bigger-tech-sustainable-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20superyachts%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20those%20yachts%20are%20too%20big%20to%20fit%20in%20Miami's%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20the%20kind%20of%20customers%20that%20are%20coming%20here%20%E2%80%94%20the%20superstars%2C%20the%20financial%20icons%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20they%20want%20privacy%2C%20they%20want%20security%2C%20they%20want%20to%20come%20and%20go%20without%20everybody%20knowing%20they're%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Nancy%20Batchelor%2C%20a%20luxury%20real%20estate%20agent%20in%20Compass%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20big%20names%20that%20have%20moved%20here%2C%20I%20know%20they're%20using%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221284bff3-42e7-4f7e-b574-0763ad45cdf7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20on%20a%20billionaire's%20radar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EILandMiami%20is%20relatively%20small%2C%20but%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETerris%20said%20the%20company%20hosts%20around%2020%20flights%20a%20month%2C%2095%25%20of%20which%20are%20for%20individuals%20seeking%20a%20landing%20pad%20for%20a%20personal%20or%20chartered%20helicopter.%20It%20takes%20three%20or%20four%20minutes%20for%20the%20aircraft%20to%20land%20and%20for%20passengers%20to%20disembark%20and%20board%20the%20boat%20that%20will%20take%20them%20to%20solid%20ground.%20Use%20of%20the%20platform%20for%20one%20landing%20costs%20between%20%244%2C000%20to%20%244%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatchelor%2C%20whose%20high-net-worth%20clients%20are%20the%20type%20to%20be%20short%20on%20time%20but%20have%20ample%20money%20to%20fly%20private%2C%20recently%20featured%20an%20ILandMiami%20helipad%20in%20a%20promotional%20video%20for%20a%20%2415%20million%20home%20on%20Miami's%20exclusive%20La%20Gorce%20Island%20set%20to%20Fergie's%20song%20%26quot%3BGlamorous.%26quot%3B%20Many%20prospective%20buyers%20own%20multiple%20homes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20an%20easy%20and%20quick%20way%20in%20and%20out%20would%20appeal%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ilandmiami%20helipad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cebb45e762ed6cfe449bf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReal%20estate%20agent%20Nancy%20Batchelor%20used%20an%20ILandMiami%20helipad%20in%20a%20recent%20marketing%20film%20for%20a%20property%20she's%20representing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nancy%20Batchelor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-private-jet-perk-benefits-luxury-travel-f1-super-bowl-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarketing%20to%20the%20billionaire%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20isn't%20easy%2C%20but%20luxury%20agents%2C%20including%20Batchelor%2C%20said%20that%20word%20is%20getting%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20reach%20out%20to%20billionaires%2C%26quot%3B