n's%20tiny%20home%20village%20in%20Eindhoven%2C%20the%20Netherlands.%20Their%20finances%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20piece%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJos%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe're%20very%20proud%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-tiny-home-house-using-chatgpt-ai-useful-guidance-was-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20our%20tiny%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%2075%2C000%20euros%20(%2487%2C000)%20without%20borrowing%20any%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-60s-built-tiny-home-mortgage-free-pros-cons-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20mortgage%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20housing%20costs%20us%20about%20800%20euros%20a%20month%2C%20including%20insurance%2C%20utilities%2C%20and%20renting%20a%20plot%20from%20Minitopia.%20After%20covering%20all%20our%20living%20expenses%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20save%20more%20than%203%2C000%20euros%20on%20average%20each%20month%20from%20a%20joint%20monthly%20income%20of%20around%205%2C500%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaving%20close%20to%2060%25%20of%20our%20income%20at%2029%20is%20uncommon%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20we%20only%20work%20three%20days%20a%20week.%20Our%20tiny%20home%20has%20given%20us%20that%20level%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-made-millionaire-steps-to-hitting-financial-freedom-early-retirement-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancial%20freedom.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser%20spent%20several%20nights%20in%20Minitopia%2C%20a%20tiny%20home%20village%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20his%20series%20exploring%20how%20living%20in%20the%20villages%20has%20affected%20residents'%20careers%2C%20lives%2C%20and%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264530b2a-4438-48c1-b3dc-1fb7e1522f7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20wanted%20a%20cheaper%20alternative%20to%20renting%20or%20buying%20in%20the%20city%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20main%20reason%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder%20was%20to%20keep%20our%20expenses%20low.%20Rent%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20is%20expensive%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-bigger-house-didnt-downsize-pros-cons-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuying%20a%20large%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20is%20even%20more%20so.%20We%20didn't%20want%20to%20stress%20about%20money%20or%20feel%20like%20we%20were%20working%20just%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJos%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20of%20my%20friends%20are%20living%20with%20their%20parents%2C%20waiting%20until%20they%20can%20afford%20a%20house.%20Others%20are%20living%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-living-by-paycheck-cant-retire-regrets-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaycheck%20to%20paycheck%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20want%20that.%20So%20we%20started%20looking%20for%20alternatives%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstruggled-to-afford-rent-built-tiny-house-middle-age-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20our%20own%20house.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20came%20across%20self-built%20tiny%20houses%20while%20scrolling%20on%20Instagram%20and%20immediately%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20perfect%20for%20us.%20They%20looked%20cute%2C%20seemed%20affordable%2C%20and%20we%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20designing%20our%20own%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20researching%20and%20found%20tiny%20home%20villages%2C%20like%20Minitopia%2C%20where%20you%20can%20rent%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20and%20build%20your%20own%20house.%20We%20visited%20them%20for%20inspiration%20and%20became%20increasingly%20excited%20about%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d149be0-52f9-4180-8024-e3a8e03b6d74%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20used%20our%20savings%20to%20fund%20building%20our%20tiny%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222831%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c59a78b87081653c9a65db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Van%20der%20Muelen%20and%20Wit's%20tiny%20home%20in%20Eindhoven.%3Cp%3ESamira%20Kafala%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJos%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20we%20started%20building%20the%20tiny%20house%20in%20May%202022%2C%20we%20moved%20into%20a%20large%20shed%20in%20my%20parents'%20backyard%20to%20save%20money.%20We%20planned%20to%20live%20there%20for%20six%20months%2C%20but%20we%20ended%20up%20staying%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20Everything%20we%20earned%20during%20that%20time%20went%20into%20the%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20find%20the%20process%20stressful%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20we%20really%20needed%20to%2C%20we%20could%20have%20asked%20our%20parents%20for%20some%20money.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20to.%20It%20just%20took%20about%20six%20months%20longer%20to%20complete%20the%20build%20than%20planned%2C%20while%20we%20saved%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba6498ac-c5a4-4868-b8ef-27195640c097%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaising%20a%20baby%20in%20a%20tiny%20home%20was%20tough%20at%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminitopia-move-tiny-home-village-son-safe-free-raise-children-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20into%20the%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202023%2C%20before%20it%20was%20completely%20finished%2C%20with%20our%20then%20seven-month-old%20son%2C%20Flip.%20Our%20second%20son%2C%20Kik%2C%20was%20born%20in%20October%202024%2C%20and%20we%20became%20a%20family%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tough%20at%20first%20because%20we%20suddenly%20had%20a%20lot%20more%20things%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20space%2C%20like%20the%20stroller%2C%20the%20crib%2C%20and%20the%20baby%20gear.%20As%20soon%20as%20Kik%20was%20old%20enough%2C%20we%20gave%20away%20what%20we%20didn't%20need%2C%20and%20it%20started%20to%20feel%20less%20cramped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222756%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20in%20tiny%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c59a57b87081653c9a65d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20live%20in%20their%20tiny%20home%20with%20two%20young%20children.%3Cp%3ESamira%20Kafala%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJos%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20underestimated%20how%20much%20clutter%20we%20owned.%20Even%20now%2C%20keeping%20a%20tiny%20home%20tidy%20can%20be%20a%20real%20challenge%2C%20especially%20with%20two%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lack%20of%20space%20also%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20host%20family%20gatherings.%20That's%20a%20downside%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-tiny-home-hurt-relationships-social-life-drawbacks-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20a%20tiny%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20it%20would%20be%20worth%20having%20a%20much%20bigger%20kitchen%20for%20the%20few%20times%20a%20year%20we'd%20host%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c56339c-ad39-46bc-a6d3-436aaffe8669%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20work%203%20days%20a%20week%20because%20our%20expenses%20are%20low%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20upsides%20is%20that%20we%20can%20both%20only%20work%20three%20days%20a%20week.%20Before%20having%20kids%2C%20I%20worked%20four%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20with%20children%2C%20that%20felt%20like%20too%20much.%20Parenting%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20energy%2C%20and%20we're%20often%20tired%2C%20so%20it%20helps%20not%20having%20to%20work%20full-time%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20wanted%2C%20one%20of%20us%20could%20afford%20to%20stop%20working%20altogether.%20We%20work%20because%20we%20want%20to%2C%20not%20because%20we%20have%20to.%20Working%20only%20three%20days%20a%20week%20means%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20home%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20which%20was%20important%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20upside%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20knowing%20we'll%20never%20be%20in%20a%20position%20where%20losing%20a%20job%20would%20mean%20losing%20our%20home.%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20mortgage%2C%20and%20we%20only%20spend%20about%20a%20third%20of%20what%20we%20earn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJos%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20your%20expenses%20are%20low%2C%20it%20takes%20away%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%20We%20still%20budget%2C%20but%20not%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20running%20out.%20We%20just%20like%20to%20keep%20costs%20down.%20We%20never%20have%20to%20turn%20something%20down%20because%20we%20can't%20afford%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20tell%20me%20to%20start%20putting%20money%20away%20for%20a%20retirement%20fund.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20wait%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffire-financial-independece-early-retirement-investing-lifestyle-boredom-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20age%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%2040%20years%20away.%20After%20all%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20myself%20working%20until%20I'm%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20I'm%20looking%20into%20using%20our%20savings%20to%20build%20another%20house%20and%20sell%20it.%20It's%20a%20way%20to%20make%20money%2C%20and%20I%20enjoy%20the%20process.%20It%20gives%20me%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFenna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20sometimes%20talk%20about%20moving%20into%20a%20bigger%20house.%20But%20I%20wouldn't%20do%20that%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20working%20more%2C%20at%20least%20not%20until%20our%20kids%20are%20in%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-toddlers-tiny-home-3-day-week-saves-income-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775296681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ccf943c02a678bd7e46d50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-toddlers-tiny-home-3-day-week-saves-income-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Things%20can%20get%20cramped%20for%20a%20couple%20raising%20young%20children%20in%20a%20tiny%20home%20village.%20They%20say%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20live%20mortgage-free%20and%20work%20less.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-toddlers-tiny-home-3-day-week-saves-income-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toaster%20Trailer%20Drops%3A%20Dark%20comedy%20led%20by%20Rajkummar%20Rao%20and%20Sanya%20Malhotra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775296527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130016884%2Cimgsize-77480.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftoaster-trailer-rajkummar-rao-and-sanya-malhotra-star-in-a-chaotic-dark-comedy-about-obsession-watch%2Farticleshow%2F130016884.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130016884.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGet%20ready%20for%20a%20rollercoaster%20of%20laughter%20in%20'Toaster'%2C%20where%20Rajkummar%20Rao%20portrays%20Ra