20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20produce%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20energy-intensive%20categories%20of%20products%20in%20most%20grocery%20stores%2C%20said%20David%20Ortega%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20the%20Noel%20W.%20Stuckman%20chair%20in%20food%20economics%20and%20policy%20at%20Michigan%20State%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%2C%20most%20direct%20impact%20on%20grocery%20prices%20is%20going%20to%20be%20through%20the%20price%20of%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20Ortega%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERising%20oil%20prices%20mean%20higher%20diesel%20prices%2C%20the%20fuel%20that%20powers%20many%20trucks%20that%20haul%20fruit%20and%20vegetables%20between%20farms%2C%20distribution%20and%20processing%20centers%2C%20and%20stores.%20Perishable%20items%20that%20need%20to%20be%20kept%20cold%2C%20from%20berries%20to%20milk%2C%20are%20being%20hit%20harder%2C%20since%20diesel%20often%20powers%20refrigeration%20systems%20on%20trailers%2C%20Ortega%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20specialty%20produce%20that%20may%20have%20to%20make%20it%20from%2C%20say%2C%20California%2C%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWholesale%20fruit%20prices%20in%20Baltimore%2C%20one%20such%20East%20Coast%20market%2C%20rose%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%20of%20USDA%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20limes%20from%20Mexico%20rose%2063%25%20between%20February%2027%2C%20the%20day%20before%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20began%20strikes%20on%20Iran%2C%20and%20March%2031%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data.%20Vine-ripe%20tomatoes%20from%20Florida%20were%20up%2051%25%2C%20while%20the%20price%20of%20blueberries%20from%20Peru%20rose%2044%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EItem%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EFeb.%2027%20Price%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMarch%2031%20Price%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EPercent%20increase%3C%2Ftd%3E%