20Donald%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20which%20affect%20some%20produce%20imports%20from%20Central%20and%20South%20America%2C%20have%20also%20increased%20wholesale%20prices%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20increases%20are%20showing%20up%20at%20retailers.%20Blueberry%20prices%20rose%2020%25%20year-over-year%20in%20the%20four%20weeks%20to%20March%2021%2C%20according%20to%20market%20research%20firm%20Nielsen%20IQ.%20Tomato%20prices%20rose%20nearly%2012%25%20at%20retail%2C%20while%20limes%20were%20up%206.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20for%20some%20produce%20that%20travels%20far%20to%20reach%20stores%2C%20such%20as%20avocados%2C%20or%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20cold%2C%20such%20as%20raspberries%2C%20were%20down%20over%20the%20same%20period.%20The%20data%20include%20prices%20at%20major%20retailers%2C%20including%20grocery%20chains%2C%20big%20box%20stores%2C%20dollar%20stores%2C%20and%20club%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20grocery%20stores%20are%20likely%20to%20pass%20most%20of%20the%20higher%20produce%20prices%20on%20to%20shoppers%20since%20they%20already%20operate%20on%20thin%20profit%20margins%2C%20said%20Phil%20Lempert%2C%20a%20food%20industry%20analyst%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20website%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supermarketguru.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESupermarketGuru%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20shelf%20life%20of%20produce%20presents%20a%20special%20problem%2C%20Lempert%20said.%20If%20retailers%20raise%20prices%20too%20much%20or%20too%20quickly%2C%20customers%20will%20simply%20buy%20elsewhere%20or%20find%20alternative%20products%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20force%20retailers%20to%20throw%20away%20rotten%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20and%20take%20a%20loss%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20really%20stuck%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20grocers'%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20milk%20or%20eggs%2C%20many%20produce%20items%20are%20discretionary%20purchases%2C%20Mani%20said.%20If%20prices%20rise%20too%20much%20or%20quality%20suffers%2C%20customers%20might%20walk%20on%20by%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20essentials%20like%20gas%20rising%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20justify%20the%20purchase%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20at%20least%20has%20to%20have%20the%20freshness%2C%26quot%3B%20Mani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20rising%20prices%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eguide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-produce-prices-rising-oil-soars-during-war-with-iran-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775295061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cfc041e762ed6cfe449ff3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-produce-prices-rising-oil-soars-during-war-with-iran-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wholesale%20prices%20for%20berries%2C%20limes%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20other%20produce%20are%20rising.%20Higher%20fuel%20prices%20from%20war%20with%20Iran%20are%20causing%20the%20increase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abit