0his%20cancer%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Charles%20Brenner%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c58d1d4133f63e1c778bd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Charles%20Brenner%20researches%20the%20relationship%20between%20metabolism%20and%20disease.%3Cp%3EKalin%20Tabov%20Photography%2FKalin%20Tabov%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDr.%20Charles%20Brenner%20runs%20a%20lab%20exploring%20the%20relationship%20between%20metabolism%20and%20disease.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20lifestyle%20factors%20can%20damage%20metabolic%20function%20and%20increase%20the%20chances%20of%20developing%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shared%20two%20lifestyle%20habits%20he%20maintains%20for%20longevity%20and%20reducing%20his%20cancer%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Charles%20Brenner%20studies%20the%20complex%20relationship%20between%20our%20metabolism%20and%20disease%20%E2%80%94%20but%20his%20lifestyle%20habits%20are%20remarkably%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrenner%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20lab%20at%20a%20City%20of%20Hope%20cancer%20center%20in%20California%2C%20researches%20NAD%2C%20which%20he%20previously%20described%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-nad-longevity-supplement-hollywood-uses-prevent-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcentral%20catalyst%20of%20all%20living%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrenner%20compared%20NAD's%20function%20to%20the%20copper%20wiring%20in%20an%20electric%20car.%20While%20food%20is%20fuel%2C%20NAD%20is%20what%20transforms%20that%20fuel%20into%20energy%20and%20other%20enzymatic%20reactions%20like%20DNA%20repair%2C%20Brenner%2C%2064%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-nad-longevity-supplement-hollywood-uses-prevent-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENAD%20naturally%20depletes%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20we%20age%2C%20research%20suggests%20certain%20lifestyle%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20like%20not%20moving%20around%20enough%20or%20eating%20too%20many%20ultra-processed%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20lowers%20levels%20faster%2C%20putting%20us%20at%20risk%20of%20developing%20diseases%20like%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20heart%20failure%2C%20and%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20Brenner%20thinks%20about%20in%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20given%20his%20work%20as%20a%20researcher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20older%20and%20being%20in%20a%20job%20where%20I%20work%20in%20an%20office%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20physical%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20along%20with%20watching%20his%20diet.%20%26quot%3BOur%20food%20and%20work%20environment%20is%20very%20conducive%20to%20weight%20gain%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrenner%20shared%20the%20two%20habits%20he%20follows%20for%20greater%20longevity%2C%20including%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-4-in-10-cancers-preventable-ways-to-lower-risk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereducing%20his%20cancer%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bbd1bc10-584b-484d-9f06-7a7d8f7ae9a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20varies%20his%20movements%2C%20from%20Orangetheory%20to%20dog-walking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walking%20dogs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6a39ee99557fb1b089fec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrenner%20said%20having%20dogs%20forces%20him%20to%20move%20more.%3Cp%3Echorkie%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrenner%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20easier%20to%20be%20sedentary%20than%20to%20be%20active%2C%26quot%3B%20thanks%20to%20our%20modern%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20humans%20no%20longer%20hunt%20or%20gather%2C%20which%20are%20very%20energy-demanding%20kinds%20of%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20paying%20to%20go%20to%20a%20gym%2C%20to%20be%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20we%20have%20to%20lift%20things%20because%20that's%20not%20part%20of%20our%20lifestyle%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20Brenner%20tries%20to%20move%20around%20as%20much%20as%20he%20can%2C%20including%20changing%20up%20his%20workout%20routine%20so%20that%20he%20stays%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tend%20to%20get%20a%20little%20bored%20with%20whatever%20gym%20thing%20I%20do%2C%20every%20six%20to%2012%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20done%20Orangetheory%2C%20I've%20done%20hot%20yoga%2C%20I%20tried%20Pilates%2C%20right%20now%20I'm%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-more-muscle-less-time-pro-tips-top-exercise-scientist-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweight%20training%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20hike%20a%20lot.%20I%20play%20tennis%20and%20go%20skiing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20helps%20him%20pack%20in%20even%20more%20steps%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Brenner's%20wife%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20athletic%26quot%3B%20marathon%20runner%2C%20and%20they%20sometimes%20run%20together.%20He%20also%20has%20two%20stepsons%20and%20two%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChasing%20around%20kids%20or%20grandkids%20is%20great%2C%20getting%20a%20dog%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Brenner%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20forces%20you%20into%20a%20physical%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af43d9d1-2bc4-4db2-973b-3e0ebefeb834%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20focuses%20on%20vegetables%20and%20avoids%20diet%20trends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fish%20with%20grilled%20vegetables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6a41a8e44c01630d31770%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222531%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrenner's%20diet%20consists%20mostly%20of%20plants%20and%20lean%20protein%20sources%20like%20fish%20and%20poultry.%3Cp%3EMisha%20Kravets%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrenner%20doesn't%20follow%20most%20diet%20trends%2C%20particularly%20the%20ones%20circulating%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20actual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-doctor-superagers-shares-anti-aging-secrets-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESuper%20Agers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20people%20who%20live%20beyond%20100%20or%20110%2C%20none%20of%20them%20follow%20these%20prescriptive%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20taking%2050%20different%20supplements%20or%20restricting%20fat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20keeps%20his%20diet%20simple.%20Brenner%20more%20or%20less%20follows%20a%20version%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%2C%20considered%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BVegetables%20are%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20Mom's%20advice%20is%20generally%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20do%20for%20longevity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20focuses%20on%20lean%20protein%20sources%20like%20poultry%20and%20fish%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mediterranean-diet-tips-dietitian-learned-greece-food-habits-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provide%20fiber%20and%20crucial%20nutrients.%20His%20favorite%20meals%20include%20fish%2C%20grilled%20vegetables%2C%20and%20fresh%20bread%2C%20or%20a%20homemade%20pizza%20with%20tomato%20sauce%2C%20artichoke%20hearts%2C%20olives%2C%20anchovies%2C%20and%20chili%20flakes%20(sans%20cheese%2C%20as%20he%20is%20lactose-intolerant).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20ties%20into%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabits-longevity-researcher-follows-for-healthy-aging-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebigger%20philosophy%20around%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cancer%20risk%20reduction%3A%20Stick%20to%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20successfully%20age%20by%20being%20physically%20active%2C%20staying%20socially%20connected%2C%20eating%20good%20food%2C%20and%20not%20obsessing%20about%20the%20small%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetabolism-researcher-longevity-habits-reduce-cancer-risk-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775294881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c58dcd4133f63e1c778bde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetabolism-researcher-longevity-habits-reduce-cancer-risk-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr.%20Charles%20Brenner%20studies%20the%20link%20between%20metabolism%20and%20disease.%20His%20habits%20include%20changing%20his%20workout%20routines%20so%20he%20doesn't%20get%20bored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetabolism-researcher-longevity-habits-reduce-cancer-risk-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Art%20investment%20is%20booming%20for%20the%20ultra-wealthy.%20But%20JPMorgan%20sees%20a%20few%20caveats%20for%20aspiring%20buyers.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222782%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22William%20Hogarth%20%C3%A2Taste%20in%20High%20Life%20being%20held%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ced32e6a864f6fcd7bced9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWiktor%20Szymanowicz%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInterest%20in%20the%20luxury%20art%20market%20is%20picking%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20buy%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20art%20doesn't%20function%20like%20a%20rational%20investing%20asset.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20senior%20lending%20specialist%20at%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank%20lays%20out%20three%20caveats%20for%20art%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20down%20years%2C%20the%20luxury-art%20market%20is%20coming%20back%20for%20ultra-wealth%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Levitt%20Reach%2C%20a%20senior%20lending%20specialist%20at%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20her%20firm's%20art-financing%20portfolio%20has%20grown%2090%25%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20Further%2C%20a%20recent%20report%20from%20Art%20Basel%20and%20UBS%20showed%20public%20and%20private%20sales%20rose%206%25%20to%20%2425%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20snapping%20two%20straight%20years%20of%20declines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20increased%20client%20interest%20in%20the%20luxury%20art%20market%20and%20in%20using%20fine%20art-backed%20lending%20to%20diversify%20liquidity%20sources%20while%20staying%20active%20in%20the%20art%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Levitt%20Reach%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-stocks-today-trump-iran-war-oil-prices-wall-street-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euncertain%20market%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alternative%20assets%20can%20be%20an%20appealing%20way%20for%20ultra-wealthy%20individuals%20to%20guard%20against%20macro%20volatility.%20To%20see%20why%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20Hermes%20handbags%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-bags-stock-market-luxury-goods-kelly-birkin-fashion-investing-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeen%20outperforming%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20buying%20art%20is%20more%20complex%20than%20picking%20a%20painting%20you%20like%20and%20hoping%20it%20increases%20in%20value%2C%20markets%20be%20darned.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20Levitt%20Reach%20laid%20out%20for%20BI%20three%20key%20caveats%20for%20art%20investing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7a87737-5e68-45be-a043-8162c9315aad%5C%22%3E(1)%20It%20doesn't%20function%20as%20a%20rational%20investment%20asset%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELevitt%20Reach%20said%20that%20while%20art%20can%20be%20a%20portfolio%20diversifier%2C%20it%20doesn't%20have%20a%20reliable%20correlation%20with%20markets%2C%20so%20shouldn't%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20hedge.%20After%20all%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20the%20value%20of%20artwork%20won't%20decline%20during%20an%20economic%20shock.%20The%20opposite%20may%20very%20well%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20noted%20that%20valuations%20are%20subjective%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20scarcity%2C%20the%20provenance%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pieces%2C%20the%20collector%20sentiment%20that%20comes%20into%20the%20factor%20of%20the%20value%20of%20the%20art.%20Whereas%20public%20markets%20are%20very%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ebe03744-ac19-4407-9f1b-79637adcd030%5C%22%3E(2)%20High%20holdings%20costs%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDisplaying%20paintings%20in%20your%20home%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20wealth%20and%20status.%20But%20for%20those%20buying%20paintings%20for%20investment%20purposes%2C%20keeping%20them%20locked%20away%20may%20make%20more%20financial%20sense%2C%20although%20that%20also%20comes%20with%20costs%20such%20as%20storage%20and%20transportation%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20clients%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-art-advisor-buying-first-piece-galleries-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epurchase%20art%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20gallery%20or%20auction%2C%20installing%20it%20is%20often%20a%20long%2C%20expensive%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20advisor%20to%20Citi's%20luxury%20art%20buying%20clients%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-advisor-citi-bank-private-wealth-clients-homes-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223717dfbb-6ec4-4cf5-9e6d-6754372bd9b5%5C%22%3E(3)%20There's%20no%20income%20generation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELevitt%20Reach%20says%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20art%20investments%20strictly%20function%20as%20a%20store%20of%20value%20and%20should%20be%20regarded%20that%20way.%20This%20contrasts%20with%20assets%20that%20produce%20yields%2C%20like%20stocks%20and%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they're%20held%20more%20for%20investment%20purposes%20you%20likely%20have%20them%20in%20storage%20facilities%20just%20to%20preserve%20the%20pieces%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20generating%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BAs%20an%20investor%2C%20that%20is%20also%20something%20very%20important%20to%20think%20about%2C%20whereas%20you%20have%20other%20options%20for%20interest%20dividends%20from%20other%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-investment-wealthy-jpmorgan-director-buyers-investing-paintings-luxury-auctions-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775294701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cfeaa0c02a678bd7e47cda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-investment-wealthy-jpmorgan-director-buyers-investing-paintings-luxury-auctions-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alexandra%20Levitt%20Reach%20of%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank%20breaks%20down%20luxu