th%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68132d97a466d2b74ab4ae56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20following%20a%20familiar%20Tesla-era%20playbook%20for%20his%20rebuilding%20plans%20at%20xAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20stakes%20are%20higher%20now%2C%20with%20a%20highly%20competitive%20AI%20environment%20and%20a%20looming%20SpaceX%20IPO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EXAI's%20cofounder%20exodus%20raises%20red%20flags%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20the%20company's%20history%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20Nordeen%20didn't%20announce%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounder-ross-nordeen-leaves-musk-preps-spacex-ipo-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleaving%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20didn't%20need%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20engineer%20was%20abruptly%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20company%20systems%20last%20week%20and%20disappeared%20from%20a%20sprawling%20group%20chat%20with%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20hundreds%20of%20other%20engineers.%20Later%2C%20he%20posted%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20hiking%20trail%20with%20the%20caption%3A%20%26quot%3BTouching%20some%20grass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENordeen%2C%20one%20of%20the%20billionaire's%20closest%20deputies%2C%20was%20the%20final%20non-Musk%20cofounder%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edepart%20the%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20eighth%20to%20exit%20in%20under%20three%20months.%20It's%20an%20unusually%20rapid%20unraveling%20of%20a%20founding%20team%20at%20a%20critical%20point%20in%20the%20company's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20SpaceX%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-sends-staff-q-and-a-on-spacex-merger-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emerged%20with%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%2C%20races%20toward%20a%20blockbuster%20IPO%2C%20the%20shake-up%20has%20become%20something%20of%20a%20spectacle.%20It%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20billionaire's%20motivations%2C%20the%20company's%20standing%20among%20competitors%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20whether%20rebuilding%20is%20simply%20an%20iteration%20of%20Musk's%20playbook%20%E2%80%94%20or%20points%20to%20deeper%20issues%20inside%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnytime%20you%20see%20mass%20departures%20of%20the%20founding%20leadership%20team%2C%20that%20is%20a%20negative%20signal%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Elson%2C%20a%20corporate%20governance%20expert%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20things%20were%20bright%20and%20rosy%20for%20the%20future%2C%20why%20would%20you%20leave%3F%20Either%20you're%20leaving%20because%20you're%20cashing%20out%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20you%20think%20the%20thing%20is%20overpriced%20or%20richly%20priced%2C%20or%20you're%20leaving%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20management%20of%20the%20organization%20going%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20way%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranco%20Granda%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20analyst%20at%20Pitchbook%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20companies%20are%20under%20increased%20scrutiny%20in%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20an%20IPO.%20While%20the%20rocket%20ship%20business%20will%20be%20the%20core%20focus%20of%20SpaceX's%20stock%20market%20debut%2C%20the%20merger%20with%20xAI%20and%20exodus%20of%20cofounders%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Blot%20of%20distractions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20integrate%20xAI%2C%20which%20is%20a%20bleeding%2C%20hemorrhaging%20business%20at%20this%20point%2C%20I%20think%20it%20creates%20a%20lot%20of%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20reports%20of%20the%20startup%20burning%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2026-01-09%2Fmusk-s-xai-reports-higher-quarterly-loss-plans-to-power-optimus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b143b714-a359-42f3-b73e-f12b06f8fa93%5C%22%3E'I%20thought%20he'd%20go%20down%20with%20the%20ship'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20some%20of%20the%2010%20cofounders%20who%20left%20before%20him%2C%20Nordeen's%20split%20was%20a%20surprise%20to%20some%20company%20insiders%20and%20close%20observers%20of%20Musk's%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20xAI%20in%202023%20from%20Tesla%2C%20where%20he%20was%20a%20technical%20program%20manager%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fashok-elluswamy-tesla-autopilot-elon-musk-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAutopilot%20team%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He's%20a%20longtime%20friend%20of%20Musk's%20cousin%2C%20James%20Musk%2C%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bthree%20musketeers%26quot%3B%20who%20assisted%20in%20Musk's%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%20takeover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20biography%20of%20the%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20colleague%20described%20Nordeen%20as%20%26quot%3BMusk's%20handler%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20he'd%20go%20down%20with%20the%20ship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20said%20he's%20rebuilding%20that%20ship.%20In%20one%20social%20media%20post%2C%20he%20said%20xAI%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20built%20right%20first%20time%20around%26quot%3B%20and%20compared%20the%20turbulence%20to%20his%20retooling%20of%20Tesla%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Musk%20ousted%20cofounder%20and%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cofounder-martin-eberhard-interview-history-elon-musk-ev-market-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Martin%20Eberhard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20followed%20out%20the%20door%20by%20cofounder%20Marc%20Tarpenning.%20Tesla%20went%20through%20two%20more%20CEOs%20before%20Musk%20took%20over%20and%20built%20a%20fledgling%20startup%20with%20a%20few%20dozen%20employees%20into%20the%20most%20valuable%20car%20company%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20turnaround%20magic%20could%20be%20difficult%20to%20replicate%20at%20xAI.%20Unlike%20Tesla%2C%20which%20had%20few%20EV%20competitors%2C%20the%20AI%20startup%20is%20operating%20in%20a%20highly%20saturated%20market.%20Though%20it's%20valued%20at%20around%20%24250%20billion%2C%20it%20lags%20behind%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20visibility%2C%20consumer%20use%2C%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20closed%20doors%2C%20Musk%20has%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20the%20progress%20on%20Grok%20Imagine%2C%20the%20company's%20image%20and%20video%20generation%20tool%2C%20and%20Macrohard%2C%20insiders%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20February%2C%20xAI%20has%20cut%20dozens%20of%20employees%20across%20the%20Grok%20Imagine%20and%20Macrohard%20teams%20and%20brought%20in%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20engineers%20to%20help%20run%20the%20company.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-macrohard-project-tesla-ai-agent-stalls-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacrohard%20project%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20saw%20several%20leads%20exit%2C%20stalled%20and%20has%20since%20become%20a%20joint%20project%20with%20Tesla%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20cofounder%20Greg%20Yang%20stepped%20down%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-loses-cofounder-tony-wu-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecofounders%20Tony%20Wu%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jimmy%20Ba%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20roles%20were%20narrowed%20%E2%80%94%20left%20the%20following%20month.%20Then%20came%20Toby%20Pohlen%2C%20who%20led%20xAI's%20computer%20use%20team%3B%20Zihang%20Dai%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20Grok%20Code%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounders-guodong-zhang-zihang-dai-depart-elon-musk-company-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGuodong%20Zhang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20led%20Grok%20Code%20and%20Grok%20Imagine.%20Manuel%20Kroiss%2C%20who%20also%20worked%20on%20the%20coding%20initiative%2C%20left%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20cofounders%20were%20fired%2C%20as%20Musk%20appeared%20to%20suggest%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2032201568335044978%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Elson%2C%20the%20corporate%20strategy%20expert%2C%20said%20the%20potential%20for%20him%20to%20consolidate%20power%20doesn't%20offset%20the%20loss%20of%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basis%20of%20the%20firm%20is%20not%20equipment%20or%20a%20patent.%20It's%20the%20intellectual%20capital%20of%20those%20who%20put%20it%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Elson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20world%20of%20AI%2C%20talent%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20precious%20assets%2C%20prompting%20fierce%20poaching%20battles%20and%20astronomical%20salaries%20paid%20to%20top%20recruits%20at%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20players%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20recruit%20that%20talent%20and%20keep%20those%20people%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Nary%2C%20a%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20expert%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20talent%20at%20the%20top%20of%20xAI%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20valuable%20part%20of%20xAI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc721394-5d50-4947-8f17-402ed6573375%5C%22%3EThe%20Musk%20playbook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20confidentially%20filed%20for%20an%20IPO%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20several%20news%20outlets%2C%20and%20could%20reportedly%20seek%20a%20valuation%20of%20%241.5%20trillion%20or%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20poised%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20ever%20IPO%20and%20beat%20Musk's%20AI%20rivals%20to%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Musk%20has%20taken%20a%20company%20public%20while%20under%20pressure.%20When%20he%20helped%20take%20Tesla%20public%20in%202010%2C%20the%20EV%20maker%20was%20cash-strapped%2C%20and%20Musk%20was%20focused%20on%20keeping%20the%20company%20afloat%20and%20getting%20its%20first%20mass-market%20vehicle%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%20who%20worked%20at%20Tesla%20during%20that%20period%20said%20executive%20shuffling%20was%20common%20then.%20Musk%20stopped%20by%20people's%20desks%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis%20and%20asked%20engineers%20to%20explain%20their%20work%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20thought%20you%20were%20full%20of%20shit%2C%20you%20were%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20recalled%20flying%20out%20to%20celebrate%20the%20IPO%2C%20watching%20Musk%20pop%20a%20bottle%20of%20champagne%2C%20and%20flying%20back%20to%20Hawthorne%2C%20California%2C%20and%20working%20later%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IPO%20%26quot%3Bwas%20almost%20seen%20as%20a%20distraction%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutive%20turnover%20has%20remained%20a%20theme%20at%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20even%20among%20acolytes%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomead-afshar-executive-tesla-profile-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOmead%20Afshar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-raj-jegannathan-departs-sales-it-vp-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERaj%20Jegannathan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20at%20xAI%2C%20the%20exodus%20of%20cofounders%20has%20become%20a%20distraction%20from%20the%20SpaceX%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20probably%20looking%20at%20this%20and%20saying%2C%20'He's%20known%20to%20do%20things%20like%20this%20and%20things%20still%20work%2C'%26quot%3B%20Pitchbook's%20Granda%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20with%20AI%20as%20it%20stands%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20could%20afford%20to%20do%20things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClearly%20they're%20trying%20to%20get%20their%20act%20together%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPO%2C%20but%20when%20you%20have%20everyone%20leave%2C%20and%20you%20have%20such%20limited%20talent%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20really%20tough%20task.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENary%2C%20the%20M%26amp%3BA%20expert%2C%20said%20the%20cofounders'%20departures%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPO%20are%20far%20from%20conventional%3B%20typically%2C%20companies%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20top%20talent%20from%20leaving%20ahead%20of%20an%20IPO.%20Then%20again%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20Musk%20himself%20is%20an%20outlier%20who%20has%20been%20known%20to%20surprise%20skeptics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20defining%20feature%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20rules%20don't%20always%20apply%20to%20a%20Musk%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20xAI%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20248-894-6012.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%