tion%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20school%20dropout%20rates%20among%20children.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-1-1757076475.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-1-1757076475-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-1-1757076475-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-1-1757076475-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-1-1757076475-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-497012%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshok%20Rathod%20started%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20to%20combat%20addiction%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20school%20dropout%20rates%20among%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20OSCAR%20gave%20her%20more%20than%20football.%20Through%20projects%20on%20health%20and%20hygiene%20with%20other%20girls%2C%20Yamini%20learned%20leadership%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20communication.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20once%20a%20boring%20girl%20with%20little%20interest%20beyond%20studies.%20I%20now%20speak%20freely%20and%20motivate%20other%20girls%20in%20my%20class%20to%20step%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20biggest%20dream%2C%20her%20eyes%20light%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20represent%20India.%20I%20want%20my%20jersey%20to%20say%20India%20on%20the%20back.%E2%80%9D%20Alongside%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20one%20day%20serve%20as%20an%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20or%20in%20the%20Navy.%20But%20her%20first%20love%20will%20always%20be%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20if%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20never%20existed%3F%20Without%20OSCAR%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20be%20nothing%2C%20just%20a%20girl%20doing%2