%3A%20fight%20malnutrition%20globally%20while%20supporting%20climate-resilient%20crops%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMid-Day%20meals%20in%20anganwadis%3A%20States%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Odisha%20now%20serve%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20malt%2C%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20jowar%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFarmer%20support%3A%20Incentives%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20and%20processing%20encourage%20rural%20economies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAwareness%20drives%3A%20Millet%20festivals%2C%20recipe%20competitions%2C%20and%20celebrity%20endorsements%20are%20changing%20perceptions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20a%20global%20conference%20hosted%20sessions%20on%20key%20millet-related%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20promotion%20and%20awareness%20among%20producers%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%3B%20value%20chain%20development%3B%20health%20and%20nutrition%3B%20market%20linkages%3B%20and%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20nutrition%3A%20Building%20food%20relationships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20both%20experts%20agree%3A%20food%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20forget%20the%20relationship%20children%20have%20with%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanchita.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20grow%20microgreens%20or%20help%20stir%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%2C%20they%20value%20food%20differently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20echoes%20this%2C%20drawing%20from%20Western%20practices%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20countries%2C%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20join%20in%20kitchens.%20Let%20them%20knead%20dough%2C%20cut%20veggies%2C%20or%20make%20pancake%20shapes.%20Even%20if%20the%20kitchen%20gets%20messy%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20likely%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20they%20