%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20handful%20of%20microgreens%20on%20a%20sandwich%20to%20a%20weekly%20batch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20small%20steps%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20For%20India%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrition%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20reconnecting%20with%20roots%2C%20celebrating%20resilience%2C%20and%20giving%20our%20children%20the%20tools%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757065097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fmicrogreens_11zon-1756194438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parents%20across%20India%20are%20rethinking%20school%20tiffins%20by%20replacing%20packaged%20snacks%20with%20nutrient-rich%20millets%20and%20microgreens.%20Easy%20to%20grow%20and%20cook%2C%20these%20superfoods%20boost%20children%E2%80%99s%20focus%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20immunity%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20fun%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20practical%20lunchbox%20staples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496778%2Fmillets-microgreens-pack-kids-healthy-lunchbox-ideas-nutrition-superfood%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20Biofortified%20Seeds%20Venture%20Is%20Transforming%2015000%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Lives%20With%20Rs%2010%20Cr%20Turnover%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20three%20years%20back%2C%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20had%20not%20heard%20about%20biofortified%20seeds%20%E2%80%93%20seeds%20that%20have%20been%20bred%20to%20have%20higher%20levels%20of%20certain%20nutrients%20like%20iron%20and%20zinc.%20The%20farmer%20has%20been%20successfully%20growing%20wheat%20on%20his%205.5-acre%20landholding%20using%20t